    • 方法详细资料

      • isMultiValue

        public boolean isMultiValue()
        Return true if the adaptee implies 0..N values can be produced and is therefore a good fit to adapt to Flux. A false return value implies the adaptee will produce 1 value at most and is therefore a good fit for Mono.

      • supportsEmpty

        public boolean supportsEmpty()
        Return true if the adaptee can complete without values.

      • isNoValue

        public boolean isNoValue()
        Return true if the adaptee implies no values will be produced, i.e. providing only completion or error signal.
